{"id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-replay-assets-9su","title":"Download real ReplayWebPage assets","description":"Add scripts/fetch-replay.sh to download ui.js and sw.js from npm/jsDelivr. Versioned and repeatable. Also add static/replay/viewer.html as the replay player shell page. Currently static/replay/ holds placeholder stubs so browser replay does not actually work.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-07-01T05:27:44.788127Z","created_by":"edsu","updated_at":"2026-07-01T05:43:46.778372Z","closed_at":"2026-07-01T05:43:46.778319Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":"rustyweb","source_repo_path":"/Users/edsu/Projects/rustyweb","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
{"id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-collections-mez","title":"Collection management","description":"Track indexed archive files in a collections.json manifest. Each entry records path, name, kind (wacz/warc), record count, file size, and SHA-256 checksum. Add rustyweb check subcommand to re-verify integrity. Fix WACZ warc_path bug (currently stores tempfile path). Add --name flag to rustyweb index.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-07-01T05:27:49.201853Z","created_by":"edsu","updated_at":"2026-07-01T05:37:27.302574Z","closed_at":"2026-07-01T05:37:27.302574Z","close_reason":"All children completed","source_repo":"rustyweb","source_repo_path":"/Users/edsu/Projects/rustyweb","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
{"id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-ui-cze","title":"Homepage and search UI","description":"Add a human-facing web UI: Google-style homepage with search box and indexed collections table, server-rendered search results page, and replay viewer that mounts <replay-web-page>. Add /files/{id} route to serve registered archive files securely.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"epic","created_at":"2026-07-01T05:27:53.287179Z","created_by":"edsu","updated_at":"2026-07-01T05:37:27.302574Z","closed_at":"2026-07-01T05:37:27.302574Z","close_reason":"All children completed","source_repo":"rustyweb","source_repo_path":"/Users/edsu/Projects/rustyweb","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0}
{"id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-collections-mez.1","title":"Fix WACZ warc_path: store source path not tempfile","description":"index_wacz currently calls index_warc(tmp.path(), ...) where tmp is a NamedTempFile, so CdxRecord.warc_path stores the temp path (e.g. /tmp/abc.warc.gz) instead of the original WACZ path. Fix: pass the original WACZ path as source_path through to index_warc so records reference the real file.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-07-01T05:28:09.477469Z","created_by":"edsu","updated_at":"2026-07-01T05:37:24.388707Z","closed_at":"2026-07-01T05:37:24.388601Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":"rustyweb","source_repo_path":"/Users/edsu/Projects/rustyweb","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-collections-mez.1","depends_on_id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-collections-mez","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-07-01T05:28:09.477469Z","created_by":"edsu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
{"id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-collections-mez.2","title":"Write collections.json manifest on rustyweb index","description":"After indexing completes, upsert an entry in {index_dir}/collections.json. Record: id (sha256 of path, first 8 hex chars), path, name, kind (wacz/warc), date_indexed, record_count, file_size, sha256 of file contents. Re-indexing the same path updates the entry.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-07-01T05:28:09.568804Z","created_by":"edsu","updated_at":"2026-07-01T05:37:24.524481Z","closed_at":"2026-07-01T05:37:24.524410Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":"rustyweb","source_repo_path":"/Users/edsu/Projects/rustyweb","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-collections-mez.2","depends_on_id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-collections-mez","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-07-01T05:28:09.568804Z","created_by":"edsu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
{"id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-collections-mez.3","title":"Add --name flag to rustyweb index subcommand","description":"Allow users to give a collection a display name at index time. Defaults to the filename stem. Passed through to the collections.json entry.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-07-01T05:28:09.643487Z","created_by":"edsu","updated_at":"2026-07-01T05:37:24.632416Z","closed_at":"2026-07-01T05:37:24.632356Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":"rustyweb","source_repo_path":"/Users/edsu/Projects/rustyweb","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-collections-mez.3","depends_on_id":"rustyweb-rustyweb-collections-mez","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-07-01T05:28:09.643487Z","created_by":"edsu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
